name: Wynwood - Factory Fresh La Grenada - Corona
additionalNotes: Crafted by Christian Eiroa, founder of the CLE cigars, the Wynwood Hills Unhinged cigar is swathed in a soft tissue to protect its delicate wrapper. The Unhinged’s binder and filler is made of premium Honduran tobacco constructed to support the exquisite USA Broadleaf wrapper. A full-bodied smoke, the Wynwood Hills Unhinged is one fine smoke that was made for the veteran cigar enthusiast or the novice wanting to step up their game.
